unlimited.fc.client.api
Interface AutoDetectInfo

public interface AutoDetectInfo

The AutoDetectInfo class provides methods to check if various transfer methods are supported on the client computer. These methods should be called after auto detection has had a chance to execute. Otherwise the default value of false will be returned, a and error messages will return an empty string.

Author:
Chris Bailey
